# Input

```md
- Top level list item 1 
- Top level list item 2
  - Nested List item 1
  - Nested List item 2
    - Sub-Nested List item 1
    - Sub-Nested List item 2

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -3,4 +3,4 @@
   - Nested List item 1
   - Nested List item 2
     - Sub-Nested List item 1
-    - Sub-Nested List item 2
+      - Sub-Nested List item 2
```

# Output

```md
- Top level list item 1
- Top level list item 2
  - Nested List item 1
  - Nested List item 2
    - Sub-Nested List item 1
      - Sub-Nested List item 2
```
